### GET all items
GET http://localhost:8080/items
Content-Type: application/json

###

### POST a new item
POST http://localhost:8080/items
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Sample Item",
  "description": "This is a new item",
  "category": "Example",
  "price": 19.99,
  "quantity": 10,
  "manufacturer": "OpenAI Inc.",
  "sku": "SKU-123456"
}

###

### PUT update an item (replace ID below with a valid MongoDB _id)
PUT http://localhost:8080/items/REPLACE_WITH_ITEM_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Sample Item",
  "description": "This item has been updated",
  "category": "Updated Category",
  "price": 24.99,
  "quantity": 15,
  "manufacturer": "OpenAI Inc.",
  "sku": "SKU-654321"
}

